g.text: Hello, my name is Justina!I am a Design Person with basic abilities in UI/UX, Design thinking and Research.Design to me is an interactive and user driven process, where it’s never complete the work of a single person alone. I design primarily with the user requirements and sustainable design in mind and enhance it by visual aesthetics. I am motivated and responsible team player who can quickly absorb new knowledge and focus on the tasks under performance and do.Basic skills include HTML/CSS, design thinking and creative problem solving.During my career I have gained skills in team building, external / internal communication and collaboration.
